{"TopicId":193468,"ForumId":51,"TopicTitle":"About Chinese Player\u0026#039;s Heart","CreatedByName":"\u5F90\u4FCA\u777F","CreatedById":204290,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-29T00:45:39Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"\u5F90\u4FCA\u777F","CreatedById":204290,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-29T00:45:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAfter playing this game for nearly half a year, I still don\u0027t know how to build rockets, but I did build over 50 other things, such as cars, boats, cannons, nuclear bombs, planes (passenger planes, fighter planes, chickens.) However, I learned a lot of scientific knowledge in the game, so I don\u0027t have to worry about my physics results in the future.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP is a very good game. I like it very much, but I am a Chinese and I don\u0027t know much English. This is my first time to play a foreign game. I can\u0027t understand many words. I hope foreign players can give me some help and look forward to the release of KSP2.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can build anything, but I can\u0027t build rockets (the bitter complaint of a Chinese player)\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-29T02:15:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223777570\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193468\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221588121139\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204290\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022\u5F90\u4FCA\u777F\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, \u5F90\u4FCA\u777F said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t understand many words.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to the forum, and congratulations on your progress, even with the language problem.\u00A0\u00A0The game includes Chinese localization but installation depends on where you bought it:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nIf it is from the store you need to download the language pack from there and install it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nIf it\u0027s from steam\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Eyou need to right click on KSP in your games list, select properties, select the tab at the top \u0027language\u0027, change to Chinese and then verify the games files:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://support.steampowered.com/kb_article.php?ref=2037-QEUH-3335\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;color:#3d6594;\u0022\u003Ehttps://support.steampowered.com/kb_article.php?ref=2037-QEUH-3335\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nIf you need any help building and flying rockets then please ask questions, you will find the members here are very friendly and helpful.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-29T20:43:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe you have difficulty understanding us, but we have no difficulty understanding you. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E Your English is fine.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd there\u0027s no rule that says you must build rockets. Lots of players don\u0027t.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidCosmos","CreatedById":192336,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-01T20:27:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223778005\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193468\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221588192984\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/30/2020 at 2:13 AM, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe you have difficulty understanding us, but we have no difficulty understanding you. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E Your English is fine.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd there\u0027s no rule that says you must build rockets. Lots of players don\u0027t.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0is right. You can build anything! For example:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlanes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRockets\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSpace Stations\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRobots\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBananas (hmmm)\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nYou have to only name it! Happy flying and have fun!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerballingSmasher","CreatedById":195689,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-01T21:30:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223779165\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193468\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221588364823\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192336\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022VoidCosmos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, VoidCosmos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBananas (hmmm)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s been done before.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mars-Bound Hokie","CreatedById":192121,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-03T17:58:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223779202\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193468\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221588368614\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022195689\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerballing (Got Dunked On)\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/1/2020 at 5:30 PM, Kerballing (Got Dunked On) said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223779165\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193468\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221588364823\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192336\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022VoidCosmos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/1/2020 at 4:27 PM, VoidCosmos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBananas (hmmm)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s been done before.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can also build something as absurd as a toilet, like one that \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/90620-vyznev/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002290620\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/90620-vyznev/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@vyznev\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0built last year.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ZtDNoiC.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/ZtDNoiC.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI also build some absurd stuff myself, like:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/Mars-Bound_Hokie/Asymmetrical-Aircraft\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EAn asymmetrical aircraft\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/Mars-Bound_Hokie/Doofenshmirtz-Evil-Incorporated\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EDoofenshmirtz Evil Incorporated\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nReplica of a building from the animated TV series \u003Cem\u003EPhineas and Ferb\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nYou don\u0027t necessarily need a rocket to build a base (unless you want to take it somewhere). If you just want to show it off, that\u0027s fine.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/Mars-Bound_Hokie/21-Rocket-Salute-Vehicle\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E21-Rocket Salute Vehicle\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/204290-%E5%BE%90%E4%BF%8A%E7%9D%BF/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022204290\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/204290-%E5%BE%90%E4%BF%8A%E7%9D%BF/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@\u5F90\u4FCA\u777F\u003C/a\u003E, I think you would be interested in the Chinese-speaking part of the KSP Forums. The \u0022International\u0022 category is specially devoted to non-English speakers who would rather use their own language when asking for help. Of course, the English-speaking players would be more than happy to assist you as well.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/forum/90-chinese-%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttps://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/forum/90-chinese-\u4E2D\u6587/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRocket-building can vary in difficulty, depending on your mission purpose. If you\u0027re just starting out, there are numerous YouTube tutorials that guide you through starting KSP. I made a couple of them last year for building your first rockets and planes (but I never got past #2). If you can\u0027t understand what I\u0027m saying, then you can at least follow what\u0027s going on in the video.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PL7ZX6GP29TTvcz1uGwXXvm5yaX_BMRwaR\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWishing you all the best.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-05-03T18:00:58Z\u0022 title=\u002205/03/2020 06:00  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EMay 3, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Mars-Bound Hokie\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}